00:12:51,900 --> 00:12:58,040
So there has to be something
that is relational in the two

250
00:12:58,040 --> 00:12:59,000
file types.

251
00:12:59,000 --> 00:13:02,880
In this case, it's saying, OK,
in orders, we found region.

252
00:13:02,880 --> 00:13:05,040
And then in people,
we found region.

253
00:13:05,040 --> 00:13:09,260
So these can work together
based on region, which is great.

254
00:13:09,260 --> 00:13:11,780
Now if I don't like
that, disagree with that,

255
00:13:11,780 --> 00:13:13,360
I can change that.

256
00:13:13,360 --> 00:13:16,940
So you do have an
opportunity to change that.

257
00:13:16,940 --> 00:13:19,320
You could also add
more fields that you

258
00:13:19,320 --> 00:13:21,540
think are also applicable.

259
00:13:21,540 --> 00:13:24,160
So you could say, OK, I'm going
