260
00:13:24,160 --> 00:13:29,120
ID here so I can create
this relationship.

261
00:13:29,120 --> 00:13:33,260
What it's not doing is joining
these together into one table.

262
00:13:33,260 --> 00:13:38,380
They're going to still
be their separate tables.

263
00:13:38,380 --> 00:13:40,880
In fact, let's go to the
worksheet right here.

264
00:13:40,880 --> 00:13:44,360
And you can still see
