266
00:13:46,260 --> 00:13:48,480
So we're not combining
those together.

267
00:13:48,480 --> 00:13:51,480
So that gives you a
lot more flexibility

268
00:13:51,480 --> 00:13:53,920
when you're dragging
and dropping and looking

269
00:13:53,920 --> 00:13:57,320
at different insights
that you might have.

270
00:13:57,320 --> 00:13:59,900
So I could put returns here.

271
00:13:59,900 --> 00:14:02,680
And then you'll
see here up there's

272
00:14:02,680 --> 00:14:09,080
nothing between people and
