273
00:14:09,080 --> 00:14:13,060
So in that case, I need to
see what fields are available

274
00:14:13,060 --> 00:14:15,560
and if there's fields
that match that.

275
00:14:15,560 --> 00:14:18,960
So I could force a
relationship here.

276
00:14:18,960 --> 00:14:21,380
Or I can say, oh, I recognize
