00:25:42,600 --> 00:25:48,640
allows you to save this anywhere
you so choose in your folder

495
00:25:48,640 --> 00:25:49,820
and then share that.

496
00:25:49,820 --> 00:25:51,640
And then that's
the file that will

497
00:25:51,640 --> 00:25:55,500
be used in this
particular visualization.

498
00:25:55,500 --> 00:25:57,640
So it's still a live connection.

499
00:25:57,640 --> 00:25:59,420
I could change that
to be an extract.

500
00:25:59,420 --> 00:26:01,330
And then it would not
go back and forth.

