503
00:26:08,040 --> 00:26:12,080
So hopefully, that helped you
get a little more familiar

504
00:26:12,080 --> 00:26:14,520
about how to connect to data.

505
00:26:14,520 --> 00:26:17,140
This is something that
students often struggle with,

506
00:26:17,140 --> 00:26:18,920
especially as they
